

<!DOCTYPE html>

<html>
<head>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <title>Page Not Found</title>
    <style>
        .NotFoundImage {
            background-repeat: no-repeat;
            background-image: url(data:image/gif;base64,);
            width: 500px;
            height: 382px;
            margin: auto;
        }
        body{
            font-family:Helvetica, Arial, 'DejaVu Sans', 'Liberation Sans', Freesans, sans-serif
        }
        h2{
            text-align:center;
            font-size:2em;
        }
        .info{
            color:#AAA;
            font-size:.8em;
            text-align:center;
        }
    </style>

</head>
<body>
    <div>
        <h2>Page Not Found</h2>
        <div class="NotFoundImage"></div>
        <div class="info">We have notified the system administrator that you've reached an invalid page.</div>

    </div>

</body>
</html>
